:keep
DataButton is a button that can be used as an ItemRenderer. Every time its vo property changes, it will try to update the data.value of the button by calling the method "getLabelForVO". If the 'vo' value is empty, it will set the "defaultValue" string as value of 'data.value' and add the styleClass 'empty'.
